    ("timescale-drop-chunk-error", "TimescaleDB Drop Chunk Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB chunk drop errors", "## Common Causes\n- Chunk still referenced by view\n- Retention policy not configured\n- Chunk too young to drop\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```sql\nSELECT drop_chunks('conditions', older_than => INTERVAL '30 days');\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM timescaledb_information.jobs WHERE proc_name = 'policy_retention';\n```"),
    ("timescale-policy-error", "TimescaleDB Policy Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB policy errors", "## Common Causes\n- Policy not enabled\n- Policy schedule wrong\n- Policy function error\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```sql\nSELECT add_retention_policy('conditions', INTERVAL '30 days');\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM timescaledb_information.jobs;\n```"),
