    ("timescale-1-node-error", "TimescaleDB Single Node Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB single node configuration errors", "## Common Causes\n- License requires multi-node for feature\n- Single node misconfigured as distributed\n- Memory not allocated correctly\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```sql\nSHOW timescaledb.license;\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM timescaledb_information.hypertables;\n```"),
    ("timescale-access-node-error", "TimescaleDB Access Node Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB access node errors", "## Common Causes\n- Access node cannot connect to data nodes\n- Foreign table not created on access node\n- Query routing failure\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM timescaledb_information.data_nodes WHERE node_type = 'access';\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM pg_stat_activity WHERE backend_type = 'timescaledb';\n```"),
    ("timescale-query-error", "TimescaleDB Query Performance Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB query performance errors", "## Common Causes\n- Query not using chunk exclusion\n- Missing index on time column\n- Full table scan instead of chunk scan\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```sql\nEXPLAIN ANALYZE SELECT * FROM conditions WHERE time > now() - INTERVAL '1 hour';\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM timescaledb_information.hypertables;\n```"),
