    ("timescale-partition-error", "TimescaleDB Partition Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB partitioning errors", "## Common Causes\n- Partition not aligned with hypertable\n- Range partition boundaries wrong\n- Partition pruning not working\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM timescaledb_information.hypertables;\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```sql\nEXPLAIN SELECT * FROM conditions WHERE time BETWEEN '2024-01-01' AND '2024-01-31';\n```"),
    ("timescale-replication-error", "TimescaleDB Replication Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB replication errors", "## Common Causes\n- Replication lag between data nodes\n- Replica node not receiving changes\n- Conflict resolution failing\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM timescaledb_information.data_nodes;\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM _timescaledb_internal._hyper_1_1_chunk;\n```"),
    ("timescale-view-error", "TimescaleDB View Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB view errors", "## Common Causes\n- View references non-existent hypertable\n- View refresh policy not set\n- View contains unsupported aggregate\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```sql\nCREATE VIEW conditions_hourly AS\nSELECT time_bucket('1 hour', time) AS bucket, device_id, AVG(temperature)\nFROM conditions\nGROUP BY bucket, device_id;\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM timescaledb_information.views;\n```"),
    ("timescale-refresh-error", "TimescaleDB Refresh Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB continuous aggregate refresh errors", "## Common Causes\n- Refresh window too large\n- Concurrent refresh conflicts\n- Refresh policy schedule wrong\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```sql\nCALL refresh_continuous_aggregate('conditions_hourly', NOW() - INTERVAL '1 hour', NOW());\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM timescaledb_information.jobs WHERE proc_name = 'policy_refresh';\n```"),
    ("timescale-config-error", "TimescaleDB Configuration Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB configuration errors", "## Common Causes\n- shared_preload_libraries missing timescaledb\n- Config parameter wrong\n- Restart required after config change\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```sql\nSHOW shared_preload_libraries;\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```bash\ngrep timescaledb /etc/postgresql/*/main/postgresql.conf\n```"),
    ("timescale-backup-error", "TimescaleDB Backup Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB backup errors", "## Common Causes\n- Backup size too large\n- Backup taking too long\n- Backup disk space insufficient\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```bash\npg_basebackup -D /backup/base -Ft -z -P\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM pg_stat_progress_backup;\n```"),
    ("timescale-restore-error", "TimescaleDB Restore Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB restore errors", "## Common Causes\n- Backup format incompatible\n- Restore target version mismatch\n- Tablespace not recreated\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```bash\npg_restore -D /backup/base -Fc\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```bash\npg_restore --list /backup/base/timescaledb.backup\n```"),
    ("timescale-upgrade-error", "TimescaleDB Upgrade Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB upgrade errors", "## Common Causes\n- Extension upgrade failed\n- PostgreSQL version incompatible\n- Migration script error\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```sql\nALTER EXTENSION timescaledb UPDATE;\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```sql\nSELECT default_version, installed_version FROM pg_extension WHERE extname = 'timescaledb';\n```"),
    ("timescale-migration-error", "TimescaleDB Migration Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB migration errors", "## Common Causes\n- Migration from vanilla PostgreSQL failed\n- Hypertable conversion error\n- Data type mismatch during migration\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```sql\nSELECT create_hypertable('mytable', 'time');\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM timescaledb_information.hypertables;\n```"),
    ("timescale-license-error", "TimescaleDB License Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB license errors", "## Common Causes\n- Community license features exceeded\n- License expired\n- Feature requires Timescale Cloud\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```sql\nSHOW timescaledb.license;\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM timescaledb_information.license;\n```"),
    ("timescale-access-node-connection-error", "TimescaleDB Access Node Connection Error", "How to fix TimescaleDB access node connection errors", "## Common Causes\n- Data node connection refused\n- Network latency too high\n- Connection pool exhausted\n\n## How to Fix\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM timescaledb_information.data_nodes;\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM pg_stat_activity WHERE backend_type = 'timescaledb';\n```"),
